## Diagnostic Categories

| Class Index | Tumour Group                             |
| ----------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| 0           | Haematolymphoid                          |
| 1           | Mesenchymal                              |
| 2           | Neuroectodermal and Neural Crest-Derived |
| 3           | Melanocytic                              |

