# рҹ§© 4. Foundation Model Embeddings

Feature embeddings extracted from pathology foundation models are stored separately.

```text
MODELS/
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Foundation_Models/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ UNI/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ train_embeddings.pkl
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ val_embeddings.pkl
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ test_embeddings.pkl
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ Virchow/
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ train_embeddings.pkl
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ val_embeddings.pkl
в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ test_embeddings.pkl
в”Ӯ
в””в”Җв”Җ
```

These embeddings are subsequently integrated into multimodal classification and survival prediction pipelines.

